# Institutional Backtest Workflow - Instruction Map

This instruction map shows how to compose core_engine components into a comprehensive institutional backtesting system using the standardized "Lego brick" architecture.

## Component Assembly for Backtesting

### Core Brick Stack
```
┌─────────────────────────────────────┐
│    HierarchicalSystemOrchestrator   │ ← System Control
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ ClickHouseDataManager               │ ← Historical Data Authority
│ RegimeEngine                        │ ← Market Condition Analysis
│ TechnicalIndicators                 │ ← Signal Processing Pipeline
│ FeatureEngineer                     │ ← ML Feature Creation
│ SignalGenerator                     │ ← Trading Signal Generation
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ CentralRiskManager                  │ ← Governance & Authorization
├─────────────────────────────────────┤
│ StrategyManager                     │ ← Strategy Orchestration
│ BacktestExecutionEngine             │ ← Historical Execution Simulation
│ PortfolioAnalytics                  │ ← Performance Measurement
│ RiskAnalytics                       │ ← Risk Assessment
└─────────────────────────────────────┘
```

